What is DevOps ?

we discuss the definition of DevOps in a simple term . So, DevOps is the culture or is the process of improving delivery's by ensuring there is proper automation, you have to ensure the quality is in place also you have to ensure proper setup of monitoring and ensured a continuous testing of the software ..

2nd Definition :
DevOps is a set of practice that automates software development process to build ,test , release and manage workloads faster and more reliable .
